<P>TRUTH and FALSHOOD: A TALE.</P>
<Q><L>Be thou as cha&s;te as Ice, as pure as Snow,</L>
<L>Thou &s;halt not e&s;cape Calumny.</L>
<BIBL>HAMLET.</BIBL></Q>
<P>LONDON: Printed for M. COOPER, in <HI>Pater-No&s;ter-Row.</HI></P>
<P>M.DCC.LV.</P>
<P>[Price SIXPENCE.]</P>
</DIV1>
